      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental hemolysis measurements shall be obtained from a minimum of three independent test runs per operating condition.",
      "rationale": "Test sample assessment is not required at MRL 2. FDA experimental data was used as the validation dataset; the number of independent replicates per operating condition in the original FDA study was not independently verified for this assessment."
    },
