    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The CFD hemolysis model meets all assessed credibility factor requirements at MRL 2. The model produces reasonably consistent hemolysis predictions across the CPB operating envelope, and the requirement that the model shall produce hemolysis predictions that are reasonably consistent with acceptable clinical performance is considered satisfied. All 7 assessed factors achieved their required levels; 6 factors were appropriately scoped as not-assessed at MRL 2. The package is accepted for submission in support of the Class II CPB device 510(k) hemolysis analysis.",
